<h3>Basic Usage</h3>
{{fa-icon 'coffee'}} (with icon name, after adding icon object to the library)<br/>
{{fa-icon icon='coffee' class='foo'}} (explictly using icon attribute, and with additional class name)
<h3>Mask with Transform</h3>
<p>(expected: black square with white dot inside, pushed to the right side)</p>
{{fa-icon icon='circle' transform="shrink-9 right-4" mask='square'}}
<h3>Default fas prefix versus specifying a different prefix for the same icon name</h3>
{{fa-icon icon='square'}}
{{fa-icon prefix='far' icon='square'}}
<h3>Missing Icon</h3>
<p>Expecting no icon between these bars |{{fa-icon icon='unfindable-icon'}}| (and a warning log in the console)</p>
<h3>Dynamic with Bound Attribute</h3>
<div>
  <p>Drag the slider to spin the magic.</p>
  {{input type='range' value=magic}}
  <div style="padding:2em;">
    {{fa-icon icon='magic' transform=(concat 'rotate-' magic)}}
  </div>
</div>
<h3>Pro Icon</h3>
<p>(If you have pro-light-svg-icons installed, this should show the 'adjust' icon in the light style)</p>
{{fa-icon prefix='fal' icon='adjust'}}
<h3>Fixed Width</h3>
<style type="text/css">
  .MistyRose {
    background-color: mistyrose;
  }
</style>
<div>{{fa-icon icon='home' fixedWidth=true class="MistyRose"}} Home</div>
<div>{{fa-icon icon='info' fixedWidth=true class="MistyRose"}} Info</div>
<div>{{fa-icon icon='book' fixedWidth=true class="MistyRose"}} Library</div>
<div>{{fa-icon icon='pencil-alt' fixedWidth=true class="MistyRose"}} Applications</div>
<div>{{fa-icon icon='cog' fixedWidth=true class="MistyRose"}} Settings</div>

